Series of annual oversized deluxe limited edition comics each collecting two issues of Rick & Morty for Local Comic Shop Day. Limited to 3000 copies.

Join degenerate superscientist Rick Sanchez as he embarks on all-new insane adventures with his awkward grandson Morty, his teenage granddaughter Summer, his veterinary surgeon daughter Beth, and his hapless son-in-law Jerry.
